<section class="about">
    <h2>About the space</h2>
    <p>
        This beautiful nineteenth-century dike house is located 15 minutes from
        Central Station. This apartment is located here, which covers 45 m2 and
        has been completely renovated...
    </p>
    <a class="text-btn">see more <span><Arrow /></span></a>

    <div id="textbox" class="textbox">
        <button id="textbox-close" class="textbox-close" aria-label="Sluiten"
            ><svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="size-6"
            >
                <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="m9.75 9.75 4.5 4.5m0-4.5-4.5 4.5M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"
                ></path>
            </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="text-container">
            <p>
                This beautiful nineteenth-century dike house is located 15
                minutes from Central Station. This apartment is located here,
                which covers 45 m2 and has been completely renovated. It is an
                old house, so it is a bit noisy. It consists of a double bedroom
                with an electrically adjustable bed and a flat-screen TV.
                Furthermore, a living room with a pleasant sitting area and a
                dining table. There is a cozy box bed (double bed) in the living
                room. The designer bathroom has an XXL bath and a walk-in
                shower. There is a separate toilet. The apartment has its own
                emergency/exit via the back. It has a Nespresso machine and a
                kettle, a refrigerator and all the necessities to make
                breakfast. There is a sink to do the dishes. Hot food cannot be
                made and I am allowed to host a maximum of 4 people. This is due
                to my permit.
                <br />
                The house is located on the monumental Nieuwendammerdijk, one of
                the top locations in Amsterdam. In the beautiful Vliegenbos, a 5-minute
                walk away, there is a tennis club. On the way you will pass Het Sluisje,
                a well-known café among Amsterdammers with a beautiful terrace where
                you can also eat.
                <br />
                From the house you can cycle to the ferry in 12 minutes, which takes
                you to Central Station in 3 minutes. From there you are within walking
                distance of all the major attractions that Amsterdam city center
                has to offer. Of course you can also take the bus to the metro, it
                leaves every 10 minutes around the corner and takes you to the metro
                in 5 minutes, the metro takes you anywhere in the city within 15
                minutes, Amsterdam is after all a small city everything is close
                by. For those who prefer peace and quiet, the Nieuwendammerdijk is
                the ideal base for the rustic North Holland Waterland. Tourist attractions
                such as Durgerdam, Volendam and Marken are within cycling distance.
                Best of both worlds, the city center is close by and so is the countryside.
                <br />
                The owner lives in the upper house. together with his 20 year old
                son and their cat. It is paid parking the costs are €9.90 per day.
                Or €1.60 per hour
                <br />
                Finally: anyone arriving at Schiphol can be picked up by the owner,
                ask for information about this. Guest access you have all the space
                for you and the rest of the guests. Only sometimes I have to use
                the washing machine. But I will talk to you first if I would use
                it if necessary Other things to look out for Violating the house
                rules will result in a fine of €
                <br />
                Registration number 03637B6FE171C6D89CC8
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
    // 1. Selecteer de knoppen en de overlay
    const openBtn = document.querySelector(".text-btn");
    const overlay = document.getElementById("textbox");
    const textBoxCloseBtn = document.getElementById("textbox-close");

    // 2. Functie om overlay te tonen
    function showOverlay() {
        overlay.classList.add("active");
    }

    // 3. Functie om overlay te verbergen
    function hideOverlay() {
        overlay.classList.remove("active");
    }

    // 4. Event listeners toevoegen
    openBtn.addEventListener("click", showOverlay);
    textBoxCloseBtn.addEventListener("click", hideOverlay);

    // 5. (Optioneel) Klikken buiten de tekst kan ook sluiten
    overlay.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
        if (event.target === overlay) {
            hideOverlay();
        }
    });
</script>

<style>
    .about {
        padding: 0 25px;
    }

    .text-btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        color: var(--primary-color);
        gap: 16px;
        padding: 16px 0 0px;
        align-items: center;
        margin-right: 4px;
    }

    .text-btn span {
        display: inline-flex;
        transform: rotate(-90deg);
        transition: transform 0.5s ease;
    }

    .text-btn:hover > span {
        transform: rotate(0deg);
    }

    .text-btn:hover {
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .textbox {
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        display: flex; /* Altijd flex */
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        cursor: zoom-out;
        z-index: 1000;
        transition:
            opacity 0.15s ease-out,
            visibility 0.15s ease-out;
        opacity: 0;
        visibility: hidden;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .textbox.active {
        opacity: 1;
        visibility: visible;
        pointer-events: auto;
    }

    .textbox-close {
        position: absolute;
        top: 16px;
        right: 16px;
        background: transparent;
        border: none;
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: var(--light-color);
        cursor: pointer;
        z-index: 1001;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .text-container {
        height: 500px;
        overflow-y: scroll;
        padding: 25px 32px;
        margin: 0 25px;
        border-radius: 14px 0 0 14px;
        background-color: var(--light-color);
    }

    /* Voor alle webkit browsers */
    .text-container::-webkit-scrollbar {
        width: 8px;
    }
    .text-container::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
        background: #f1f1f1;
    }
    .text-container::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
        background: var(--primary-color);
    }
    .text-container::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
        background: #555;
    }

    /* Safari-specifieke aanpassing */
    .text-container {
        scrollbar-width: thin; /* Voor Firefox */
        scrollbar-color: var(--primary-color) #f1f1f1; /* Voor Firefox */
    }

    /* Safari scrollbar altijd zichtbaar maken */
    .text-container::-webkit-scrollbar {
        -webkit-appearance: none;
        width: 8px;
    }

    .textbox p {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
    }

    .textbox-close svg {
        width: 48px;
        height: auto;
    }

    .textbox-close:focus {
        outline: 2px solid #fff;
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 544px) {
        .about {
            padding: 0 40px;
            max-width: 90%;
        }
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
        .about {
            padding: 0 25px 0 80px;
            border-right: solid 1.5px var(--primary-color);
            max-width: 40%;
        }
    }

    @media screen and (min-width: 1224px) {
        .about {
            padding: 0 50px 0 120px;
        }
    }

    /* @media screen and (min-width: 1424px) {
    } */
</style>
